{"tid":1938117,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美大學紫外線消毒口罩重用","createTime":"2020-03-22T10:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T15:23:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc73287ed206740598db780fc20417b57041b9b","tid":1938117,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200322/EE3FOI72DFOIOZ7TD4C4YFTSDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200322%2FEE3FOI72DFOIOZ7TD4C4YFTSDY%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdEtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=c916c2b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200322%2FEE3FOI72DFOIOZ7TD4C4YFTSDY%2F&h=6ca6cdcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200322/EE3FOI72DFOIOZ7TD4C4YFTSDY/</a><br />\n<br />\n美大學紫外線消毒口罩重用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200322/large/1584807850_8b9c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200322%2Flarge%2F1584807850_8b9c.gif&h=5574605f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用作消毒的紫外線燈。<br />\n<br />\n美國多間醫院因武漢肺炎疫情令口罩嚴重短缺之際，內布拉斯加州大學醫療中心上周四開始實驗程序將口罩消毒重用，但方法不是香港某政客介紹的「以100℃高溫翻蒸」，而是使用紫外線燈。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：澳門籲市民勿來港<br />\n<br />\n稱不會破壞口罩<br />\n<br />\n重用口罩幾乎無人認為是最理想辦法，但眼見醫療中心的口罩只剩數星期存量，中心傳染病部主管魯普（Mark Rupp）表示這是「無辦法中的辦法」，並解釋數據清楚顯示「紫外線照射殺菌法」有效殺死和令病毒不活躍，也不會破壞口罩，希望藉此令每個口罩能使用一星期，甚至更久。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，該中心數年前曾以紫外線清潔治療過感染伊波拉病毒病人的房間，方法亦十分簡單，只要把燈開着並離開，房間三至五分鐘後就完成消毒。研究人員表示若不採用這方法，醫護人員只能設法收好口罩，不作清洗，然後多次使用，但會增加口罩被污染的風險。<br />\n<br />\n不過，口罩註明只能使用一次，醫院提供重用口罩予員工可能違法。美國疾控中心（CDC）上周四晚就突然發出新指示，稱「在沒有辦法，或必要」的情況下，醫院可提供美國國家職業安全研究所沒有批准使用的口罩，似乎為重用口罩「開綠燈」。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》"},{"pid":"8e254ff527d5c8d624b249538bdf32599aad37bc","tid":1938117,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"伽瑪射線會唔會更加有效 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08537f42ff26d450254587908f9454d9a32201ba","tid":1938117,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"美國醫院唔究口罩用?因為中國扣起晒?"},{"pid":"8bf2d13b409b0bb1995450c7813c48f0e6fb1922","tid":1938117,"uid":336922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93245ce1e9e960ee4742272441de4c882842c2cc","tid":1938117,"uid":287269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08537f42ff26d450254587908f9454d9a32201ba","tid":1938117,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"美國醫院唔究口罩用?因為中國扣起晒?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"係，3M係大陸生產都唔俾運。加埋大陸人由一月已經不斷搶"},{"pid":"9bd4437f89e1400313cc03085404ce4efa456bc7","tid":1938117,"uid":84702,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93245ce1e9e960ee4742272441de4c882842c2cc","tid":1938117,"uid":287269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08537f42ff26d450254587908f9454d9a32201ba","tid":1938117,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"美國醫院唔究口罩用?因為中國扣起晒?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"係，3M係大陸生產都唔俾運。加埋大陸人由一月已經不斷搶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:06:43.000Z","msg":"仲有香港人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de0baed4e3318f32d8909bbb5668283a1bcbedd","tid":1938117,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3a04e7b1d310afb084aad287e9db3daadc0722","tid":1938117,"uid"